title: [Rumor Woods, Caravan Trail]
[Caravan Trail]
description: The narrow path abruptly ends where the high cliffs sharply veer to the northeast, widening the view of rock-strewn bluegrass hills gently rolling toward the snowy mountains.  Yurts are arranged in semicircles around small fires, each cozy grouping flanked by either plum or cobalt banners.  A thin layer of hoarfrost, glittering in the sunlight, clings like flock to the needles of the scant whitebark pines peppering the landscape.
